articles.title: Remains found in search for 12-year-old following reported crocodile attack in Australia - CNN
articles.description: Australian police believe they have found the remains of a 12-year-old child reportedly attacked by a crocodile while swimming in a creek in the Northern Territory, they said on Thursday.
